description:
&lt;p&gt;Day Surgery Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;North West London – Brentford TW8&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Riverside Clinic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary: £40,000 - £45,000 (dependent on experience)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthshare is a successful provider of clinical and diagnostic services to the NHS and private sectors across various locations throughout the country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Riverside Clinic is opening a new Day Surgery Unit, which comprises of 8 beds, 1 theatre, 4 Recovery Bays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Day Surgery Lead, you will be managing the Day Surgery 8 bedded ward ensuring a safe, efficient and effective service is provided to patients and consultants users. You will provide leadership and direction to the Day Surgery team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role includes clinical practice, human resources management which covers staffing and performance management, and financial management and procurement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will ensure that professional and national standards are met and will act as a positive role model to junior staff following Nursing and Midwifery Council guidelines and recommendations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide leadership and management for Day Surgery department&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strong partnerships with key stakeholders both internally within Healthshare and externally e.g. consultants, local NHS Trusts etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build effective methods for the management of the Nursing, ODP and HCA staff, using objectives and action plans for continuous skills improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the Key Performance Indicator targets are achieved by the Day surgery ward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure that equipment needed is available and in good working condition with an effective maintenance plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide effective deployment of resources needed to sustain agreed activity levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please see Job Description for full details and personal specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Like the sound of this role? Don’t miss out – apply now!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
